一、Redis配置文件解析
  1、常用配置
    -port 6379
    -bind 127.0.0.1
    -tcp-backlog 511
    -timeout 0
    -tcp-keepalive 300
    -daemonize yes
    -databases 16
    -logfile /var/log/redis_6379.log
    -maxclients 10000
    -dir /var/lib/redis/6379
  2、内存管理
    1）内存清除策略
    -volatile-lru
    -allkeys-lru
    -volatile-random
    -allkeys-random
    -volatile-ttl
    -noeviction
    
    2）选项默认设置
    -maxmemory <bytes>
    -maxmemory-policy noeviction
    -maxmemory-samples 5
    
    
三、部署LNMP+Redis
    /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx -t  //检查配置
